S.FORM: Dalibor Bagari nalecuhan i Munich, West Germany, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw. Dalibor Bagari i 2000 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 24, namapili' tu nu Chicago Bulls putiput. 2 bulad 7 demiad, 1980 a mihca, Dalibor Bagari , miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
